tasks.description:
Create TypeScript types and API client functions for all 34 Compliance endpoints.

## File 1: `packages/api-client/src/compliance-types.ts`

Define ALL types from the discovery report:

### Type Aliases (34 total)
```typescript
export type ComplianceAreaCode = 'URE' | 'RODO' | 'AML' | 'KSH' | 'ESG' | 'LABOR' | 'TAX' | 'CONTRACT' | 'INTERNAL_AUDIT';
export type MatterType = 'new_regulation' | 'regulation_change' | 'audit_finding' | 'incident' | 'license_renewal' | 'contract_review' | 'policy_update' | 'training_need' | 'complaint' | 'inspection' | 'risk_assessment' | 'other';
export type MatterStatus = 'open' | 'researching' | 'analyzed' | 'action_plan_ready' | 'in_progress' | 'review' | 'completed' | 'closed' | 'on_hold';
export type MatterPhase = 'initiation' | 'research' | 'analysis' | 'planning' | 'document_generation' | 'approval' | 'training' | 'communication' | 'verification' | 'monitoring' | 'closed';
export type Priority = 'low' | 'medium' | 'high' | 'critical';
export type RiskLevel = 'low' | 'medium' | 'high' | 'critical';
export type Likelihood = 'very_low' | 'low' | 'medium' | 'high' | 'very_high';
export type Impact = 'negligible' | 'minor' | 'moderate' | 'major' | 'catastrophic';
export type RiskColor = 'green' | 'yellow' | 'orange' | 'red' | 'critical';
export type ObligationType = 'reporting' | 'licensing' | 'documentation' | 'training' | 'audit' | 'notification' | 'registration' | 'inspection' | 'filing' | 'other';
export type Frequency = 'one_time' | 'daily' | 'weekly' | 'monthly' | 'quarterly' | 'semi_annual' | 'annual' | 'biennial' | 'on_change' | 'on_demand';
export type ComplianceStatus = 'compliant' | 'partially_compliant' | 'non_compliant' | 'unknown' | 'not_applicable';
export type DocType = 'policy' | 'procedure' | 'form' | 'template' | 'register' | 'report' | 'certificate' | 'license' | 'contract_annex' | 'training_material' | 'communication' | 'regulation_text' | 'internal_regulation' | 'risk_assessment' | 'audit_report' | 'other';
export type DocStatus = 'draft' | 'review' | 'approved' | 'active' | 'superseded' | 'expired' | 'archived';
export type SignatureStatus = 'not_required' | 'pending' | 'partially_signed' | 'signed' | 'expired';
export type TrainingType = 'mandatory' | 'awareness' | 'certification' | 'refresher' | 'onboarding';
export type TrainingStatus = 'planned' | 'material_ready' | 'scheduled' | 'in_progress' | 'completed' | 'cancelled';
export type TrainingRecordStatus = 'assigned' | 'notified' | 'started' | 'completed' | 'overdue' | 'exempted';
export type DeadlineType = 'filing' | 'reporting' | 'license_renewal' | 'audit' | 'training' | 'review' | 'inspection' | 'payment' | 'document_expiry' | 'contract' | 'custom';
export type DeadlineStatus = 'pending' | 'in_progress' | 'completed' | 'overdue' | 'cancelled';
export type RaciRole = 'responsible' | 'accountable' | 'consulted' | 'informed';
export type RiskStatus = 'open' | 'mitigated' | 'accepted' | 'closed';
```

### Interfaces (15 total)
- ComplianceArea { code, name_pl, name_en, governing_body, key_regulations: string[], risk_level, responsible_person_id, status }
- ComplianceMatter { id, title, matter_type, area_code, priority, status, phase, description?, legal_analysis?, risk_analysis?: Record<string, unknown>, obligations_report?, consequences_report?, action_plan?: Record<string, unknown>[], communication_plan?: Record<string, unknown>[], source_regulation?, created_at, updated_at, completed_at? }
- ComplianceObligation { id, area_code, title, obligation_type, frequency, next_deadline?, responsible_person_id?, compliance_status, penalty_description?, penalty_max_pln?, created_at }
- ComplianceDeadline { id, title, date, type, status, recurrence, area_code, area_name, days_overdue? }
- ComplianceDocument { id, title, doc_type, area_code, matter_id?, version, generated_by, approved_by?, approved_at?, valid_from?, valid_until?, review_due?, signature_status, status, created_at }
- ComplianceTraining { id, title, area_code, matter_id?, training_type, content_summary?, target_audience: string[], deadline?, status, created_at }
- TrainingRecord { person_id, person_name, status, notified_at?, completed_at?, score? }
- ComplianceRisk { id, risk_title, risk_description?, likelihood, impact, risk_score, color, current_controls?, mitigation_plan?, status, matter_id?, area_code, matter_title?, created_at }
- RaciEntry { id, area_code?, matter_id?, person_id, person_name, role, notes? }
- ComplianceDashboard { total_obligations, compliant_count, non_compliant_count, open_matters, overdue_deadlines, at_risk_areas, overall_risk_score }
- RiskHeatmapArea { code, name, risk_count, avg_score, max_score, critical_count, color }
- RiskHeatmapResponse { areas: RiskHeatmapArea[], total_risks, overall_avg }
- WeeklyReportArea { code, name, obligations: { compliant, partially_compliant, non_compliant }, matters: { opened, closed }, deadlines: { met, missed }, documents: { generated, approved }, open_risks }
- WeeklyReportResponse { generated_at, areas: WeeklyReportArea[], whatsapp_sent }
- ScanResult { scanned_chunks, regulatory_found, matters_created, details: { title, area_code, matter_type, priority, matter_id, action }[] }

### Request body interfaces
- CreateMatterRequest { title, matter_type, area_code, description?, priority?, contract_id?, source_regulation? }
- CreateObligationRequest { area_code, title, obligation_type, frequency?, next_deadline?, responsible_person_id?, description?, penalty_description?, penalty_max_pln? }
- GenerateDocRequest { matter_id, doc_type, title?, template_hint?, signers?: { name, role }[], valid_months?: number }
- CreateTrainingRequest { title, area_code, matter_id?, training_type?, content_summary?, target_audience?: string[], deadline?, generate_material?: boolean }
- CreateRaciRequest { area_code?, matter_id?, person_id, role?, notes? }

## File 2: `packages/api-client/src/compliance.ts`

Create async functions for all 34 endpoints. Follow existing pattern from `people.ts` / `intelligence.ts`:

```typescript
import { customFetch } from './base';
import type { ... } from './compliance-types';
```

Functions needed:
- fetchComplianceDashboard() → { ...ComplianceDashboard }
- fetchComplianceAreas() → { areas: ComplianceArea[] }
- fetchComplianceArea(code: string) → ComplianceArea (with linked data)
- fetchMatters(params?: { status?, area_code?, priority?, limit? }) → { matters: ComplianceMatter[] }
- createMatter(data: CreateMatterRequest) → ComplianceMatter
- fetchMatter(id: number) → ComplianceMatter
- researchMatter(id: number, query?: string) → research results
- advanceMatter(id: number, forcePhase?: string) → ComplianceMatter
- generateMatterReport(id: number) → report string
- generateCommPlan(id: number) → communication plan
- executeComm(id: number) → execution summary
- fetchObligations(params?: { area_code?, status?, limit? }) → { obligations: ComplianceObligation[] }
- fetchOverdueObligations() → ComplianceObligation[]
- createObligation(data: CreateObligationRequest) → ComplianceObligation
- fulfillObligation(id: number, evidenceDescription?: string) → ComplianceObligation
- fetchDeadlines(params?: { days_ahead?, area_code? }) → { deadlines: ComplianceDeadline[] }
- fetchOverdueDeadlines() → ComplianceDeadline[]
- fetchDocuments(params?: { area_code?, doc_type?, status?, limit? }) → { documents: ComplianceDocument[] }
- fetchStaleDocuments(days?: number) → ComplianceDocument[]
- generateDocument(data: GenerateDocRequest) → ComplianceDocument
- approveDocument(id: number, approvedBy?: string) → ComplianceDocument
- signDocument(id: number, signerName: string) → ComplianceDocument
- fetchTrainings(params?: { status?, area_code?, limit? }) → { trainings: ComplianceTraining[] }
- fetchTrainingStatus(id: number) → { training: ComplianceTraining, records: TrainingRecord[] }
- createTraining(data: CreateTrainingRequest) → ComplianceTraining
- completeTraining(id: number, personId: number, score?: number) → TrainingRecord
- fetchRisks(params?: { area_code?, status?, limit? }) → { risks: ComplianceRisk[] }
- fetchRiskHeatmap() → RiskHeatmapResponse
- fetchRaci(params?: { matter_id?, area_code? }) → { raci: RaciEntry[] }
- upsertRaci(data: CreateRaciRequest) → { raci_id, person_id, role }
- fetchDailyReport() → { report: string | null }
- fetchWeeklyReport() → WeeklyReportResponse
- fetchAreaReport(code: string) → full area report
- scanRegulatory(hours?: number) → ScanResult

